Synopsis:            Parse GPX files
Description:         Parse GPS Exchange (GPX) files using HXT into data structures.
Homepage:            http://code.google.com/p/geo-gpx/
Category:            Utils
Author:              Tony Morris
Maintainer:          code@tmorris.net
Copyright:           2009 Tony Morris
